{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "本章承接上章，燕南飞在鲜花美人间饮酒作乐，与美人谈论蔷薇与死亡的哲学。三更时分燕南飞遣散众人，面对傅红雪。两人展开了一场关于生死、心愿、信义的深度对话。燕南飞一年前败于傅红雪刀下，被给予一年时间了结心愿，如今如约赴死。傅红雪试图再给他一年时间，但燕南飞宁死不愿透露心愿。傅红雪的刀即将出鞘时，金球突袭，木头人和泥人两名侏儒刺客上下夹攻燕南飞，傅红雪出刀击退刺客。泥人和木头人对话中透露他们是受人指派而来，任务失败回去也是死。本章展现了燕南飞的悲壮豪迈和傅红雪的冷酷中暗含的温情。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_mei_ren",
      "text": "因为蔷薇有刺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ren",
      "speaker_name": "美人",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你喜欢刺？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_mei_ren",
      "text": "我喜欢刺人，刺人的手，刺人的心。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ren",
      "speaker_name": "美人",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "这理由不好，我不喜欢听。",
      "tone": "不满",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_mei_ren",
      "text": "你喜欢听什么？",
      "tone": "询问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ren",
      "speaker_name": "美人",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "当然要。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_mei_ren",
      "text": "据说在很久很久以前，第一朵蔷薇在很远很远的地方开放的时候，有一只美丽的夜莺，因为爱它竟不惜从花枝上投池而死。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ren",
      "speaker_name": "美人",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "这故事真美！可惜太悲伤了些。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_mei_ren",
      "text": "你错了。死，并不是件悲伤的事。只要死得光荣，死得美，死又何妨？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ren",
      "speaker_name": "美人",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "今天早上，我也想采几枝蔷薇给你。我费了很多时候，才拴在我的衣带里。衣带却已松了，连花都系不起！花落花散，飘向风中，落入水里。江水东流，那些蔷薇也随水而去，一去永不复返。江水的浪花，变成了鲜红的，我的衣袖里，却只剩下余香一片。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ren",
      "speaker_name": "美人",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你闻一闻，我一定要你闻一闻，作为我们最后的一点纪念。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你来了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我来了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "我知道你会来的！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我当然会来，你当然知道，否则一年前你又怎会让我走？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "现在一年已过去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "整整一年。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "好长的一年。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "好短的一年。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你觉得这一年太长，只因为你一直在等，要等着今天。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我没有等！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "虽然我明知今日必死，但我却不是那种等死的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "就因为你有很多事要做，所以才会觉得这一年太短？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "实在太短。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "现在你的事是否已做完？你的心愿是否已了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "一年前，我败在你的刀下！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "也许你本不该败的，只可惜你人太年轻，剑法却用老了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "那时你就问我，是不是还有什么心愿未了？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "我问过！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "那时我就告诉过你，纵然我有心愿未了，也是我自己的事，我自己的事，一向都由我去做。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "我记得。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "那时我也告诉过你，你随时都可以杀我，却休想逼我说出我不愿的事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "现在……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "现在我还是一样！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "一样不肯说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你借我一年时光，让我去做我自己想做的事，现在一年已过去，我……",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你是来送死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不错，我正是来送死的！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "所以现在你已经可以杀我了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "一年前此时此地，我就可以杀了你！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你让我走，只因为你知道我必定会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你若不来，我只怕永远找不到你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "很可能。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "但是你来了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我必来！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "所以你的心愿若未了，我还可以再给你一年。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "不必！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "不必？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我既然来了，就已抱定必死之心！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你不想再多活一年？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "大丈夫生于世，若不能锄强诛恶，快意恩仇，就算再多活十年百年，也是生不如死！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "可是你的心愿还未了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "谁说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "我说的，我看得出。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "纵然我的心愿还未了，也已与你无关。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "可是我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你本不是个多话的人，我也不是来跟你说话的！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你只求速死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你宁死也不肯把你那未了的心愿说出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我宁愿死在自己的剑下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "我知道！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "但你还是要用你的刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "你有不肯做的事，我也有。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我死了后，你能不能善待我这柄剑？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "text": "剑在人在，人亡剑毁。你死了，这柄剑也必将与你同在。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "燕南飞",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "请！请出手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_ren",
      "speaker_name": "泥人",
      "listener": "char_mu_tou_ren",
      "text": "都是你害我，你算准这一着必定不会失手的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_tou_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木头人",
      "listener": "char_ni_ren",
      "text": "我算错了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_ren",
      "speaker_name": "泥人",
      "listener": "char_mu_tou_ren",
      "text": "算错了就该死。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_tou_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木头人",
      "listener": "char_ni_ren",
      "text": "这件事做不成，回去也一样是死，倒不如现在死了算了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_ren",
      "speaker_name": "泥人",
      "listener": "char_mu_tou_ren",
      "text": "你想怎样死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_tou_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木头人",
      "listener": "char_ni_ren",
      "text": "我是个木头人，当然要用火来烧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
